{"word":"Cord","slug":"cord","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Cord</b> Ancient uses of:<br/> - In casting lots<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=2&verse=5'>Mic 2:5</a> <br/> - Fastening tents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=18'>Exo 35:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=40'>Exo 39:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=54&verse=2'>Isa 54:2</a> <br/> - Leading or binding animals<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=118&verse=27'>Psa 118:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=11&verse=4'>Hos 11:4</a> <br/> - Hitching to cart or plough<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=39&verse=10'>Job 39:10</a> <br/> - Binding prisoners<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=15&verse=13'>Jdg 15:13</a> <br/> - Measuring ground<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=2'>2Sa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=14'>Jos 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=55'>Psa 78:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=7&verse=17'>Amo 7:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=2&verse=1'>Zec 2:1</a> <br/> - Worn on the head as a sign of submission<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=31'>1Ki 20:31</a> <br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of spiritual blessings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=16&verse=6'>Psa 16:6</a> <br/> - Of sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=5&verse=22'>Pro 5:22</a> <br/> - Of life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=12&verse=6'>Ecc 12:6</a> <br/> - Of friendship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=4&verse=12'>Ecc 4:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=11&verse=4'>Hos 11:4</a> <br/> Symbolic uses of:<br/> - Token in mourning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=33'>1Ki 20:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=36&verse=8'>Job 36:8</a> <br/> - Signifying an inheritance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=14'>Jos 17:14</a> "}]}